  "keyFeatures": [
    "5,727 Spanish-language clinical Q&A pairs derived from 63 obstetrics/gynaecology PDFs",
    "Three ready-to-use dataset variants: sft_grounded, sft_closed_book, and qa_flat_jsonl",
    "Reproducible 8-step pipeline: PDF extraction → cleaning → chunking → enrichment → QA generation → quality control → evaluation → publication",
    "Ragas-based quality evaluation with faithfulness and answer-relevancy scores across all splits",
    "QLoRA fine-tuning scripts for Gemma 4 and MedGemma 1.5 4B with TRL + PEFT + bitsandbytes",
    "Document-level train/validation/test split to prevent data leakage",
    "Full auditability: every QA pair is traceable to its source PDF, pages, and chunk",
    "Published on Hugging Face Hub (JhonHander/obstetrics-qa-synthetic-es)"
  ],
